@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_boegut(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp((v0 + (v1 + 0.62 * tmp + 0.35)))
    v2 = (((v0 + 0.67 * v1 + 0.54) / v1) - ((v0 + 0.71 * v1 + 0.32) * (v0 + 0.44 * v0 + 0.96)))
    v0 = wp.abs(v2)
    v0 = v2
    tmp = v2
    v1 = ((wp.exp(v0 + 0.24) / wp.abs(v1 + 0.70)) + wp.sin(v1))
    data[tid] = v0
